== [[Noun]] ==
# A pulley mechanism for lifting heavy loads.
# The act of hoisting.
# The [[perpendicular]] [[height]] of a [[flag]], as opposed to the [[fly]], or
[[horizontal]] [[length]], when flying from a [[staff]].
# The height of a [[fore-and-aft]] [[sail]], next the [[mast]] or [[stay]].

----

===[[Transitive verb]]===
# To [[raise]]; to [[lift]]; to elevate; especially, to raise or lift to a desired [[elevation]], by means of [[tackle]] or [[pulley]], as a [[sail]], a [[flag]], a heavy [[package]] or [[weight]].

